title: Rusko Discography - Vinyl rips + Fabriclive + Remixes + sets
description:
This is my Rusko Discography - ALL Vinyls and vinyl that he has featured on has been ripped, including promo cd's and a few mixes and ofcourse, Fabrivlive37 - the Caspa and Rusko mix CD.

Rusko is big in the Dubstep scene, and usually can be found working closely with dubstep producer "Caspa" who together made the Fabriclive37 mix cd.Check my other torrents to see my Caspa Discography

ALL vinyl rips and tracks have full Artwork for all details.
